{
  "stem": "19111.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was an outhouse, like-- you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they felt that they didn't want to give it to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They just did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just threw it in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the Germans discovered that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they selected a group of people, who-- made them undress completely.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had to go in into the latrine, up to their necks in this-- and fish out all the jewels and everything that was put in there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the-- we were all on a roll call, standing in the field.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Nazis passed by-- you, you, you, you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they picked on one elderly man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was with his son.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His son was next to him too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the son begged that he should-- he wants to go instead of his father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So what they did instead, they made him join his father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they went both to this filthy job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they were starting to assign to these huts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were actually in the ground, cut out a long path.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we didn't have any beds or anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was just we laid on-- on the-- actually, on the ground.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had some straw spread out there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that we were assigned-- each one was assigned to a separate-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they called it a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't how to express what I saw, but they called it a barrack.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's what it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "A barrack.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And a few days later, some people have committed some minor thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But a roll call was called.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they put up a gallow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I remember five people were hanged in front of everybody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We all had to stand and watch.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
